6
00:00:20,373 --> 00:00:21,202
Merci.

7
00:00:21,728 --> 00:00:22,522
De rien.

8
00:00:24,291 --> 00:00:25,576
Je dois y aller.

9
00:00:26,405 --> 00:00:27,304
A plus tard.

10
